{"tw": {"2253970": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "原型勇者", "steam_appid": 2253970, "required_age": "18", "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253970/extras/136cc34c790f370baf298245f5f6a2e4.avif?t=1745576921\" width=620 height=200 /></span>《原型勇者》是一款橫向卷軸動作遊戲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲中你將要要扮演代號「勇者」的戰鬥員，進入地下城搜尋任務目標。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用你精湛的操作擊敗怪物和頭目，取得各種戰利品和新招式，提升實力並查出真相吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253970/extras/97e0a9d9b2a17a26275785af6fbf752d.avif?t=1745576921\" width=640 height=540 /></span>傳說，遠古時期，某個擁有強大魔力的「魔女」對世界的人們降下了難以解除的詛咒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >而你，勇敢的戰鬥員「勇者」，為了幫助全人類擺脫「詛咒」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接下了討伐魔女的任務，獨自前往地下城...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253970/extras/e0b548950d89dd48a67a80f49596a542.?t=1745576921\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253970/extras/e0b548950d89dd48a67a80f49596a542.poster.avif?t=1745576921\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span>隨著你的一次次涉險，地下城的樣貌和埋藏的隱密逐漸被揭開</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但關於魔女，關於「詛咒」的真相卻愈發撲朔迷離...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >到底誰才是你的敵人？究竟是誰在說謊？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >擊敗眼前的敵人，變強，然後找出答案吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >擊敗各具特色的敵人和魔王，取得他們的招式變強吧！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253970/extras/220655a1e38ac